First Uranium Says Board Begins Review of Business as Simmers Sells Stake

-- B y   V i c t o r i a   B a t c h e l o r
-- 
2011-07-13T02:11:41Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-07-13/first-uranium-says-board-begins-review-of-business-as-simmers-sells-stake.html
First Uranium Corp. (FIU)  said that,
following the announcement by Village Main Reef that it intends
to sell its 26 percent interest in First Uranium, the board has
empowered a committee of directors to monitor developments and
undertake a review of the company and its capital structure.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Victoria Batchelor at 
 vbatchelor@bloomberg.net  